data.description: Owners have an assumable FHA loan, contact me for more information. 2 Year First American Home Warranty included!  Recently remodeled ranch on 3.62 acres, features a beautiful kitchen with custom cabinetry and concrete countertops, the perfect place to set your inner chef free. Hearth room off the kitchen perfect for a cup of coffee or glass of wine. Vaulted ceilings, open floor plan welcome you home. Primary suite offers a 9x12 walk-in closet and stunning private bathroom. 3 additional bedrooms and 2 full baths. Enjoy this summer on your large covered stamped concrete patio. Great views of the plains. Country living complete with detached 720 sq/ft garage and 30x32 insulted, heated and air-conditioned shop with 10ft doors. This is a property you will not want to miss.
